{
  "rationale": "The supervisor uses systematic sweeping with rotation to ensure efficient coverage, introduces a 'sweeping' state to alternate between coverage lines, and strictly prevents forward movement when obstacles are detected. All uncontrollable events are handled in every state. Oscillation is avoided by preferring lateral rotation and a full rotation when stuck.",
  "new_states": [
    "clear",
    "obs_front",
