  "coverage_strategy": [
    "Begin in 'clear' state and move forward into 'sweeping' for systematic coverage.",
    "On obstacle detection, rotate away from the obstacle rather than backing up, to avoid oscillation.",
    "Use 'sweeping' to represent active coverage lines, returning to 'clear' for re-alignment.",
    "If surrounded (multiple obstacles), perform a full rotation to find a new path.",
    "Never allow moving forward when any obstacle is detected.",
    "Switch between clockwise and counterclockwise rotations to avoid repeated patterns."
